title: Hampton Yount
description: Hampton Yount (Nerdist podcast! Bob and Tom! Winner of the DC Improv Comedy Competition!) is such a great YMIW guest. Stories that have stuck in Pete's head for WEEKS after, and so so many laughs and real moments. Gosh, a real cooker. "Gosh, a real cooker" is also available as a t-shirt on youmadeitweird.com. Just kidding. Unless you want it. "GARC." Enjoy, you weirdos!!
